    "One significant advantage of deep learningbased video watermarking methods is their superior ability to effectively address video watermarking challenges, such as motion and compression artifacts, surpassing the capabilities of conventional approaches.Although numerous papers referenced in this study employ various embedding techniques, it is not possible to definitively determine the optimal solution for the video watermarking process.",
